ne}}\n\n{{Buddhism topics}}\n\n[[Category:Locations in Buddhist mythology]]\n[[Category:Mythological kingdoms, empires, and countries]]\n[[Category:Tibetan Buddhism]]\n[[Category:Theosophy]]\n[[Category:Shambhala Vision]]\n[[Category:Mythological places]]\n[[Category:Pure lands]]\n", "name_user": "Cnwilliams", "label": "safe", "comment": "Disambiguated:Nathan Drake\u2192Nathan Drake (character)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shambhala"}
